WEBVTT

01:40.380 --> 01:48.740
[You are My Fateful Love]
[EP17]

01:55.979 --> 01:56.699
What's wrong?

01:59.619 --> 02:00.380
Did you get beaten up?

02:18.539 --> 02:19.539
What's wrong with you?

02:23.739 --> 02:24.819
Mr. Xu

02:26.100 --> 02:27.180
protected me

02:27.419 --> 02:28.780
from being beaten up,

02:29.259 --> 02:30.299
but in my spirit,

02:30.299 --> 02:31.780
he dealt me a crushing blow.

02:32.739 --> 02:34.019
This is normal.

02:34.019 --> 02:35.780
Mr. Xu is a gifted speaker.

02:36.340 --> 02:39.419
When he negotiates with the other party,

02:39.419 --> 02:41.660
he is able to exploit his opponent's weaknesses.

02:42.220 --> 02:43.380
So what are your plans?

02:47.859 --> 02:48.660
I decided...

02:50.620 --> 02:51.859
Faithful words grate upon the ear.

02:52.539 --> 02:54.180
I have decided to follow

02:54.460 --> 02:55.380
Mr. Xu's advice

02:56.259 --> 02:57.299
and save up some money first.

02:58.539 --> 02:59.500
What do you think

03:00.500 --> 03:01.579
about me making a living from singing?

03:02.180 --> 03:03.220
For example, performing in bars

03:03.579 --> 03:04.579
or doing live streams.

03:04.780 --> 03:06.220
Are you sure you can save money this way?

03:13.859 --> 03:14.699
I just want to sing a song.

03:14.699 --> 03:15.579
Is it so hard?

03:15.819 --> 03:17.060
If you just want to sing,

03:17.060 --> 03:18.060
it's really not hard.

03:18.299 --> 03:19.380
But if you want to

03:19.739 --> 03:20.620
let singing be your means of

03:20.620 --> 03:21.780
making a living

03:22.060 --> 03:23.859
or even want to achieve something,

03:24.660 --> 03:25.419
it's really

03:26.780 --> 03:27.380
hard.

03:29.019 --> 03:30.139
However, I believe that

03:31.739 --> 03:33.019
as long as you've made up your mind

03:33.940 --> 03:34.780
and aren't afraid of the challenges,

03:36.299 --> 03:37.180
then do it.

03:39.660 --> 03:40.859
After all, you only live once.

03:55.780 --> 03:57.460
You really are my best mate.

03:58.660 --> 03:59.180
Okay.

04:00.100 --> 04:01.460
But isn't our relationship

04:01.460 --> 04:02.699
moving a little too fast?

04:02.859 --> 04:04.180
It's fast-paced time!

04:04.620 --> 04:06.460
Okay, okay, you eat an apple,

04:06.460 --> 04:07.819
you eat an apple to calm your shock.

04:10.539 --> 04:11.819
Okay, just figure it out.

04:18.299 --> 04:19.259
[When interacting with others,]

04:19.539 --> 04:20.979
[it is important to remember to put yourself in their shoes.]

04:21.859 --> 04:22.620
[Sometimes,]

04:23.060 --> 04:24.179
[what you perceive as kindness]

04:24.939 --> 04:26.499
[may come across as controlling to the other person;]

04:28.379 --> 04:29.499
[what you see as pursuing your dreams]

04:30.100 --> 04:31.859
[may seem like fooling around to them;]

04:34.059 --> 04:35.100
[and what you consider...]

04:37.660 --> 04:38.900
I can assure you,

04:40.260 --> 04:40.900
Xu Huaisong

04:40.900 --> 04:42.580
didn't think of you like that at all.

04:44.499 --> 04:45.660
Not only did he not think so,

04:48.379 --> 04:49.780
but he thought you were cute.

04:52.140 --> 04:53.340
[What you think is a social faux pas]

04:54.340 --> 04:56.140
[might actually be quite endearing to others.]

04:59.700 --> 05:00.979
What are you thinking, Ruan Yu?

05:03.859 --> 05:05.460
Your skill is not very good.

05:06.780 --> 05:07.939
Fortunately, the flaws don't hide the advantages.

05:08.260 --> 05:09.220
My beauty

05:09.220 --> 05:10.059
hasn't been affected.

05:10.059 --> 05:10.499
Come on,

05:10.499 --> 05:11.539
take a photo of me again.

05:11.820 --> 05:13.539
You really are repaying kindness with ingratitude.

05:13.820 --> 05:14.739
Yeah, yeah.

05:14.739 --> 05:15.979
Don't take a photo of me from below.

05:15.979 --> 05:16.820
Let's start.

05:18.859 --> 05:22.900
Flying starlight

05:24.020 --> 05:24.939
turned into...

05:25.859 --> 05:26.939
Hello, great writer.

05:27.939 --> 05:28.859
What are you recording?

05:29.460 --> 05:30.020
I

05:30.020 --> 05:31.340
registered a video account.

05:31.340 --> 05:32.340
I asked him to record

05:32.340 --> 05:33.660
a video of me singing.

05:34.179 --> 05:35.179
I just heard.

05:35.580 --> 05:36.460
Nice singing!

05:36.700 --> 05:37.739
Compared to the original singer,

05:37.820 --> 05:38.939
your rendition has a different feel to it.

05:39.619 --> 05:40.660
I wish you every success.

05:41.059 --> 05:42.020
Miss Ruan,

05:42.419 --> 05:44.299
you actually listen to Shican's songs too?

05:45.859 --> 05:46.700
Occasionally.

05:47.140 --> 05:47.939
Tasteful.

05:48.260 --> 05:49.460
Follow me, follow me.

05:49.939 --> 05:50.739
No problem!

05:51.499 --> 05:51.939
Come on!

05:51.939 --> 05:53.179
Let's find a place to enjoy

05:53.179 --> 05:54.059
it again.

05:54.059 --> 05:55.419
Why are you so narcissistic?

05:55.539 --> 05:56.260
You go and record a better video for him.

05:56.260 --> 05:57.660
Actually, I'm quite handsome,

05:57.660 --> 05:58.739
but there is a little problem with the angle.

05:58.739 --> 05:59.499
Adjust it.

06:02.820 --> 06:05.220
How can you be so narcissistic?

06:10.539 --> 06:11.580
Have you had dinner yet?

06:18.419 --> 06:19.020
Yes.

06:19.859 --> 06:20.499
So early.

06:21.780 --> 06:22.820
Cai made rice cakes.

06:23.100 --> 06:23.900
I just ate a little.

06:24.419 --> 06:25.340
I'm not hungry now.

06:26.299 --> 06:27.379
You go and eat with them.

06:28.100 --> 06:29.979
What about tomorrow?

06:31.220 --> 06:32.140
You can't have

06:32.619 --> 06:33.780
tomorrow's dinner.

06:39.580 --> 06:40.460
Tomorrow?

06:42.979 --> 06:43.939
Who knows

06:43.939 --> 06:44.619
what tomorrow will bring?

06:45.979 --> 06:47.460
Have dinner or not,

06:49.100 --> 06:51.299
it depends on my mood tomorrow.

07:04.660 --> 07:05.340
Shican,

07:05.859 --> 07:07.100
tomorrow's itinerary  has been released.

07:07.419 --> 07:08.460
You need to put on your make-up at five in the morning

07:08.460 --> 07:10.140
and start shooting magazines at six thirty on time.

07:10.340 --> 07:11.020
You probably have a thirty minute break

07:11.020 --> 07:12.379
after the shoot.

07:12.539 --> 07:14.260
You have to rush to record a variety show at 7:30,

07:14.260 --> 07:15.900
which will take about eight to nine hours,

07:15.900 --> 07:17.340
and then live broadcast at 8:00 in the evening.

07:17.660 --> 07:18.619
Didn't I say I don't want to appear on variety shows

07:18.739 --> 07:20.260
and do live-streamed product sales?

07:24.140 --> 07:25.499
I know you're tired now.

07:25.660 --> 07:27.539
But actor should seize more opportunities

07:27.539 --> 07:29.059
and appear in public,

07:29.140 --> 07:29.780
so people won't

07:29.780 --> 07:30.499
forget about you.

07:32.179 --> 07:33.619
It's not a matter of tiredness.

07:35.780 --> 07:36.539
I just...

07:37.379 --> 07:38.299
I don't even have

07:38.299 --> 07:39.059
time to write songs.

07:40.580 --> 07:41.619
Writing songs?

07:42.179 --> 07:42.739
Last time,

07:42.739 --> 07:43.780
didn't I give you time?

07:43.780 --> 07:44.780
I let you rest for a week.

07:45.499 --> 07:46.820
Didn't the song be written either?

07:57.340 --> 07:59.780
It's hard for people to stay in the limelight forever.

08:00.419 --> 08:01.220
If you don't catch

08:01.220 --> 08:02.179
your golden age,

08:02.660 --> 08:03.260
I'm afraid you won't even have the chance

08:03.260 --> 08:04.379
to sing in the future.

08:30.619 --> 08:32.820
It's hard for people to stay in the limelight forever.

08:33.220 --> 08:35.260
If you don't catch your golden age,

08:35.660 --> 08:36.460
I'm afraid

08:36.460 --> 08:38.059
you won't even have the chance to sing in the future.

08:52.859 --> 08:53.700
[I got the milk tea]

08:53.700 --> 08:54.779
[from Shican today.]

08:55.019 --> 08:55.859
[So happy!]

08:56.139 --> 08:57.019
[Come on, Shican!]

08:58.220 --> 08:58.820
[Shican,]

08:59.340 --> 09:00.180
[I am a Starlight from]

09:00.180 --> 09:01.499
[Shen'ao Village.]

09:02.060 --> 09:03.739
[I sang your famous song today.]

09:04.100 --> 09:05.820
[It's on my homepage and please guide me.]

09:14.659 --> 09:17.180
Flying starlight...

10:00.739 --> 10:02.060
[Your voice is very distinctive.]

10:02.180 --> 10:03.300
[It's also very emotional.]

10:03.540 --> 10:04.619
[But the vocal skills still need]

10:04.619 --> 10:05.899
[to be improved.]

10:06.100 --> 10:06.619
[And]

10:06.700 --> 10:07.659
[if you really love,]

10:07.820 --> 10:08.739
[please stick with it.]

10:09.300 --> 10:10.420
[I will give you this sentence.]

10:10.619 --> 10:11.580
[To myself too.]

10:34.019 --> 10:36.220
Li Shican replied to me!

10:37.700 --> 10:40.180
Li Shican replied to me!

11:02.899 --> 11:04.340
Li Shican!

11:06.139 --> 11:07.859
Li Shican!

11:08.820 --> 11:10.700
Li Shican!

11:38.460 --> 11:40.220
Mr. Xu, you got up too early.

11:40.659 --> 11:41.220
Good morning!

11:41.580 --> 11:42.979
I have a dinner engagement tonight,

11:43.019 --> 11:44.180
so we have to start early.

11:45.139 --> 11:46.340
Mr. Xu is truly worthy of being the top of

11:46.340 --> 11:46.899
the lawyer

11:46.899 --> 11:47.460
with judgmental personality traits.

11:47.460 --> 11:48.100
Early in the morning,

11:48.100 --> 11:49.379
you even have planned dinner.

11:50.139 --> 11:50.859
The opportunity is reserved for

11:50.859 --> 11:51.739
the prepared.

11:52.779 --> 11:53.739
Mr. Xu, don't worry,

11:53.739 --> 11:54.700
I'm ready too.

11:55.259 --> 11:56.220
Today's return visit need to

11:56.220 --> 11:57.220
feedback to everyone.

11:57.340 --> 11:58.220
The legal opinion,

11:58.220 --> 11:59.619
I have sorted it out and printed it out.

12:10.979 --> 12:11.899
Good job!

12:13.060 --> 12:13.859
Thank you, Mr. Xu.

12:14.899 --> 12:15.499
You see.

12:16.499 --> 12:17.859
In fact, there are some cases here that are

12:17.859 --> 12:19.300
quite representative.

12:19.659 --> 12:21.580
There are many intangible heritage workshops and

12:21.580 --> 12:22.820
intangible heritage artisans in the ancient town.

12:23.060 --> 12:23.940
They frequently

12:23.940 --> 12:25.019
encounter intellectual property disputes

12:25.300 --> 12:25.739
in their work

12:25.739 --> 12:27.460
and personal lives.

12:27.739 --> 12:28.180
Right.

12:28.259 --> 12:29.180
I remember a paper cutter telling

12:29.180 --> 12:30.659
me that he had created a series of

12:30.659 --> 12:32.340
original patterns.

12:32.619 --> 12:33.460
As a result, it didn't take long

12:33.460 --> 12:34.259
for the Internet to appear,

12:34.259 --> 12:35.379
exactly the same pattern.

12:35.659 --> 12:37.420
And have been used in various places.

12:37.580 --> 12:38.420
However, it is difficult to maintain rights

12:38.420 --> 12:39.779
because there is no copyright registration application

12:39.779 --> 12:41.379
in advance.

12:41.540 --> 12:42.180
Yes.

12:42.659 --> 12:43.379
These craftsmen have been passing on culture

12:43.379 --> 12:45.019
all their lives.

12:45.139 --> 12:46.460
Then, as a lawyer,

12:46.460 --> 12:48.259
we should try our best to protect them.

12:49.100 --> 12:50.859
In this way, you should work harder.

12:51.420 --> 12:52.139
The popularization of intangible heritage

12:52.139 --> 12:53.139
copyright

12:53.139 --> 12:54.139
should also be sorted out.

12:54.420 --> 12:56.379
Including the conditions and

12:56.379 --> 12:57.220
procedures of copyright declaration,

12:57.220 --> 12:58.379
you should make articles with pictures and texts,

12:58.379 --> 12:59.859
easy to understand,

12:59.859 --> 13:00.779
and send them to

13:00.779 --> 13:01.460
the WeChat official account of our town.

13:01.460 --> 13:02.420
No problem.

13:02.779 --> 13:03.540
Okay, go ahead.

13:04.100 --> 13:05.060
Okay.

13:08.420 --> 13:09.379
I'll go first, Mr. Xu.

13:09.979 --> 13:10.420
Okay.

13:11.499 --> 13:13.659
How did you come here alone today?

13:14.379 --> 13:15.820
What about the lawyer who always

13:15.820 --> 13:17.619
goes with you?

13:18.540 --> 13:19.499
He went on a visit.

13:21.019 --> 13:23.220
And he and I

13:23.420 --> 13:24.979
are not a pair relationship.

13:26.180 --> 13:27.220
Then today,

13:27.779 --> 13:29.379
you're here to lobby again, aren't you?

13:29.739 --> 13:31.659
No, Mr. Li.

13:32.180 --> 13:34.259
I'm here specifically for you today.

13:37.540 --> 13:39.779
These days,

13:39.859 --> 13:41.540
I have visited many intangible heritage workshops.

13:41.979 --> 13:42.820
I found that

13:43.019 --> 13:44.420
there are many craftsmen

13:44.420 --> 13:45.460
in this town, all like you.

13:45.859 --> 13:47.139
They have inherited the skills of their elders and

13:47.139 --> 13:48.979
masters since they are children.

13:49.180 --> 13:49.979
In this workshop,

13:49.979 --> 13:51.259
you have stayed for decades.

13:52.060 --> 13:53.779
But I also heard someone say that

13:53.859 --> 13:55.420
the times are different now.

13:55.779 --> 13:56.859
The next generation of artisans are

13:56.859 --> 13:57.659
fewer and fewer.

13:58.220 --> 13:59.259
Many intangible heritage cultures

13:59.259 --> 14:00.779
are at risk of being lost.

14:01.659 --> 14:02.499
I

14:02.659 --> 14:04.019
also want to do my part for

14:04.019 --> 14:05.180
intangible heritage inheritance.

14:05.859 --> 14:06.619
So,

14:06.739 --> 14:07.859
I intend to

14:07.940 --> 14:09.659
write a new book on this topic

14:10.300 --> 14:12.019
with a writing style that is

14:12.019 --> 14:12.899
close to the youth of today and

14:13.259 --> 14:14.379
to pass on the beauty of

14:14.379 --> 14:15.700
traditional culture.

14:16.779 --> 14:19.180
Do you think I can do it?

14:20.779 --> 14:22.619
Just for your eloquence yesterday,

14:23.340 --> 14:24.619
who dares to say no?

14:25.460 --> 14:26.739
But I can't do

14:26.739 --> 14:27.700
it on my own.

14:28.060 --> 14:29.180
To tell a story,

14:29.180 --> 14:30.859
I must first understand the story,

14:31.220 --> 14:33.499
so I have to learn from you first

14:33.659 --> 14:35.180
about the pyrographic gourd.

14:46.580 --> 14:48.420
About the pyrographic gourd,

14:49.060 --> 14:49.940
it is right that

14:50.220 --> 14:51.659
you find me.

14:52.700 --> 14:54.619
But you saw it all.

14:54.779 --> 14:56.259
I have too much works.

14:56.979 --> 14:58.379
Not so much free time.

14:58.820 --> 15:00.540
I can only say it once.

15:04.859 --> 15:05.540
Mr. Li,

15:05.940 --> 15:07.058
do you mean

15:07.259 --> 15:08.659
that you're willing to be interviewed today?

15:10.379 --> 15:11.060
Great.

15:11.060 --> 15:13.259
Daddy, Daddy.

15:17.460 --> 15:19.100
Why are you putting a hidden weapon on me again?

15:20.499 --> 15:21.940
Miss Ruan, you are here too.

15:23.180 --> 15:23.739
Dad.

15:25.340 --> 15:26.659
What are you doing here?

15:27.100 --> 15:28.420
Aren't you going to sue me?

15:28.700 --> 15:29.540
You sue.

15:30.060 --> 15:32.060
Isn't there a lawyer to mediate this?

15:32.659 --> 15:34.180
Miss Ruan happens to be here.

15:35.100 --> 15:35.779
My...

15:37.739 --> 15:39.340
My sincere apologies to you.

15:39.619 --> 15:40.820
Dad, I'm sorry.

15:41.019 --> 15:41.700
I was wrong.

15:41.859 --> 15:43.379
I was the one who was fooling around.

15:44.259 --> 15:46.180
Why did you figure it out today?

15:46.899 --> 15:48.460
Dare I stand here today,

15:48.659 --> 15:50.180
I must have been thought

15:50.180 --> 15:51.180
clearly.

15:51.779 --> 15:52.300
You

15:53.899 --> 15:55.100
take a look at this first.

15:58.259 --> 15:58.779
Come on.

16:01.859 --> 16:03.700
This is my idol, Li Shican,

16:03.700 --> 16:04.940
said about me.

16:06.460 --> 16:08.739
Every word, every sentence

16:09.259 --> 16:11.259
all contain...No...

16:12.220 --> 16:14.259
are full of recognition for me.

16:15.019 --> 16:17.700
I admit that before that

16:18.259 --> 16:20.180
I'm like a guy on a blind path,

16:20.379 --> 16:22.259
a wild child exploring in a daze.

16:22.659 --> 16:23.859
But today is different.

16:24.340 --> 16:26.300
My idol's recognition of me

16:26.420 --> 16:27.899
illuminated the road of my dream.

16:28.180 --> 16:28.820
From today onwards,

16:28.820 --> 16:30.139
I'm not a wild child.

16:30.139 --> 16:31.259
Wild child!

16:31.540 --> 16:33.060
If I kill you today,

16:33.060 --> 16:34.420
won't I even be able to kill relatives for

16:34.420 --> 16:35.259
the sake of righteousness?

16:35.379 --> 16:36.779
Don't be angry, Mr. Li.

16:36.979 --> 16:38.220
When you get sick, no one can replace you.

16:38.259 --> 16:39.859
If you get angry to death, nobody will be pleased.

16:39.859 --> 16:41.460
It's both mentally draining and physically exhausting.

16:42.379 --> 16:43.979
Sit down, Dad.

16:44.259 --> 16:45.139
Today,

16:45.700 --> 16:47.220
I'm not here to argue with you.

16:49.659 --> 16:50.420
I know

16:51.139 --> 16:53.060
you and mom gave birth to me quite late in life.

16:54.460 --> 16:55.899
When my mom leaves,

16:57.340 --> 17:00.220
you and my sister are worried about me.

17:00.540 --> 17:02.940
You always want me by your side,

17:02.940 --> 17:03.940
safe and secure.

17:04.499 --> 17:05.940
You always think I won't grow up.

17:06.739 --> 17:08.580
But one day I'll grow up.

17:10.540 --> 17:11.859
And I'm not too young.

17:13.580 --> 17:14.859
I hope my dream

17:15.659 --> 17:16.540
and the path of my life can

17:16.540 --> 17:17.820
be chosen by myself.

17:21.259 --> 17:22.139
Dad, I've figured it out.

17:23.340 --> 17:24.300
If you don't support or approve

17:24.300 --> 17:25.740
my dream,

17:26.179 --> 17:26.899
it doesn't matter.

17:27.500 --> 17:28.899
I can still hold on.

17:30.340 --> 17:32.980
But if you support me,

17:34.300 --> 17:35.580
I will be very happy.

17:42.780 --> 17:44.939
Time waits for no one.

17:45.300 --> 17:46.340
I went to save money.

17:46.340 --> 17:47.139
I still have to report the loss

17:47.139 --> 17:48.219
and replace my ID card.

17:48.939 --> 17:49.699
I'm leaving, Dad.

17:51.060 --> 17:51.780
Stop.

17:53.540 --> 17:55.100
Dad, you don't have to keep me.

17:55.740 --> 17:56.780
You can't keep someone

17:56.780 --> 17:58.139
who must leave.

17:58.219 --> 18:01.619
I have to save money and reissue my ID card.

18:02.780 --> 18:04.419
Don't you need money to reissue your ID card?

18:05.659 --> 18:06.340
Take it!

18:18.820 --> 18:19.619
Dad.

18:20.820 --> 18:23.619
You're willing to support me?

18:24.020 --> 18:25.219
Or still testing me?

18:25.340 --> 18:26.820
Am I bored?

18:27.820 --> 18:29.540
Your path is your choice.

18:30.300 --> 18:32.580
We're happy for you success.

18:33.219 --> 18:36.020
Don't blame others if you can't be successful.

18:36.540 --> 18:37.699
Miss Ruan, come on.

18:38.020 --> 18:39.699
Ignore someone who is leaving.

18:40.100 --> 18:41.219
Let's go ahead.

18:57.100 --> 18:57.820
Scared me to death.

18:57.820 --> 18:59.419
What are you doing without anyone noticing?

18:59.820 --> 19:00.459
Sister,

19:01.300 --> 19:02.899
please help me take a good look.

19:03.580 --> 19:04.179
Is this really

19:04.179 --> 19:05.219
my ID card?

19:05.820 --> 19:06.899
It's not fake, is it?

19:08.580 --> 19:09.300
You're stupid.

19:11.100 --> 19:12.219
It's not yours. It's mine.

19:14.020 --> 19:15.219
Dad told me yesterday,

19:16.020 --> 19:17.260
as long as you have the heart to endure hardship,

19:17.659 --> 19:18.580
he will let you go.

19:18.939 --> 19:19.740
Don't stop.

19:27.020 --> 19:28.020
I'm free.

19:31.820 --> 19:32.820
I'm free.

19:33.820 --> 19:34.740
You're not happy?

19:38.740 --> 19:39.459
I'm free.

19:43.419 --> 19:44.740
I'm free.

19:45.100 --> 19:46.580
Free! Free! Free!

19:47.139 --> 19:48.699
I'm free.

19:50.100 --> 19:51.699
I'm free!

19:51.820 --> 19:53.100
I will pack my bags.

19:53.820 --> 19:56.060
Take whatever you

19:56.060 --> 19:57.459
want to suffer.

19:57.699 --> 19:59.219
What I suffer is not necessarily a hardship,

19:59.500 --> 20:00.419
maybe it's a pleasure.

20:06.419 --> 20:08.020
Mr. Li, I'll leave first.

20:08.020 --> 20:08.500
Okay, I'll listen to your lecture

20:08.500 --> 20:09.780
another day.

20:11.740 --> 20:12.219
Bye.

20:12.699 --> 20:13.379
Bye.

20:19.100 --> 20:20.379
Hello, do you need some help?

20:21.100 --> 20:21.939
Thanks.

20:22.179 --> 20:22.659
Come on.

20:28.419 --> 20:29.219
Change direction,

20:32.699 --> 20:33.419
Doesn't matter?

20:34.100 --> 20:35.300
Thank you. Thank you.

20:35.300 --> 20:36.899
Are you okay?

20:37.740 --> 20:38.020
Sister, your cage drawer

20:38.020 --> 20:39.580
is too high,

20:39.580 --> 20:40.500
so you have to be careful.

20:40.820 --> 20:42.500
Yes, I was careless.

20:43.219 --> 20:44.659
Her father has been sick recently.

20:45.020 --> 20:46.419
I am so busy every day

20:46.419 --> 20:47.379
that I am fainted.

20:47.740 --> 20:49.100
The electric car forgot to charge too.

20:49.379 --> 20:50.859
Are you going to set up your stall?

20:51.619 --> 20:52.100
Right.

20:52.379 --> 20:53.139
I made it all myself.

20:53.139 --> 20:54.139
Some rice cakes.

20:54.300 --> 20:55.939
I'm ready to sell it in the snack street.

20:55.939 --> 20:57.980
Mom, you're so tired.

20:58.179 --> 20:59.659
Let's not go today.

21:00.139 --> 21:01.020
The Chinese New Year is coming soon.

21:01.020 --> 21:02.500
There are many people on the street.

21:02.619 --> 21:04.419
Besides, I have finished making rice cakes.

21:05.300 --> 21:06.619
How many rice cakes do you have?

21:15.179 --> 21:16.659
It seems that tonight's

21:16.659 --> 21:17.659
dinner is rice cake again.

21:18.980 --> 21:20.500
Is it a virtue to help others?

21:20.820 --> 21:22.020
But it can't be based on

21:22.020 --> 21:23.419
wasting food.

21:24.179 --> 21:25.379
So since you bought

21:25.379 --> 21:26.300
it, eat it all.

21:26.540 --> 21:26.939
Mr. Xu, what about the dinner you

21:26.939 --> 21:28.340
said in the morning?

21:28.619 --> 21:29.260
It's all gone to pot.

21:32.619 --> 21:33.699
Pot?

21:34.659 --> 21:36.419
That's a pretty good idea.

21:37.540 --> 21:39.020
If you just eat rice cakes,

21:39.340 --> 21:40.780
it's a little too dry indeed.

21:41.500 --> 21:43.939
Otherwise, just soak in the soup

21:43.939 --> 21:45.179
and eat it together.

21:45.619 --> 21:46.300
Okay.

21:47.020 --> 21:48.020
Whatever soup you

21:48.020 --> 21:48.820
want, I'll make it.

21:49.699 --> 21:52.300
I'd like to have tomato potato brisket soup.

22:15.219 --> 22:16.500
Why did you come to Shen'ao?

22:18.619 --> 22:19.939
Are you here for the event?

22:21.139 --> 22:21.659
No.

22:21.820 --> 22:22.899
I came here specifically for you.

22:24.419 --> 22:25.980
Mr. Xu, I'm not seeing things, am I?

22:26.699 --> 22:27.980
Isn't that Li Shican?

22:28.980 --> 22:29.500
Miss Ruan is actually a

22:29.500 --> 22:31.139
friend of a big star.

22:32.300 --> 22:32.820
What kind of friends

22:32.820 --> 22:33.780
do you say they are?

22:35.619 --> 22:36.780
Should they be...

22:38.139 --> 22:38.780
No.

22:42.379 --> 22:43.060
Have you forgotten

22:43.060 --> 22:43.980
that you still owe me a meal?

22:44.939 --> 22:45.859
I didn't forget.

22:46.500 --> 22:47.139
But

22:47.340 --> 22:49.020
you tell me your itinerary

22:49.020 --> 22:50.219
directly, I can go

22:50.219 --> 22:50.780
and find you.

22:50.780 --> 22:51.780
Why do you run to this far place.

22:52.379 --> 22:53.780
Then I've come here,

22:53.780 --> 22:55.500
so I'll take a break here for a few days.

22:55.699 --> 22:57.139
Just for a few more meals.

22:58.020 --> 22:58.619
No problem.

22:59.780 --> 23:01.260
I'll take you to drop off your luggage first.

23:01.419 --> 23:01.980
Good.

23:02.820 --> 23:05.020
The environment here is particularly good.

23:05.500 --> 23:06.820
I'll take you around later.

23:07.260 --> 23:08.219
Why is Mr. Xu running?

23:08.219 --> 23:09.379
Aren't we proper residents?

23:09.379 --> 23:10.379
We came first.

23:10.619 --> 23:12.020
There's no need to make way for the big star.

23:14.100 --> 23:15.219
You have a point.

23:16.899 --> 23:17.699
Go back to your room first.

23:17.820 --> 23:18.340
Here.

23:19.500 --> 23:20.580
It will also be very comfortable.

23:20.899 --> 23:22.100
Be careful.

23:34.580 --> 23:35.459
Mr. Xu,

23:35.619 --> 23:37.459
you went too slowly.

23:38.179 --> 23:39.020
You're slow.

23:39.619 --> 23:40.340
I've been waiting for you

23:40.340 --> 23:41.020
here for a while.

23:42.500 --> 23:44.100
Wait for me to do what?

23:46.780 --> 23:48.980
You just said she owed you a meal.

23:50.219 --> 23:50.820
Yeah.

23:51.260 --> 23:52.060
Does this have anything

23:52.060 --> 23:52.899
to do with Mr. Xu?

23:52.899 --> 23:53.939
Of course.

23:54.580 --> 23:55.780
I owe her a meal too.

23:57.419 --> 23:58.699
That night's hot pot.

24:01.219 --> 24:02.100
So what?

24:04.340 --> 24:05.260
So now it's me,

24:05.260 --> 24:06.419
owing you a meal.

24:09.820 --> 24:11.020
I owe you a meal.

24:11.219 --> 24:12.340
You owe him a meal.

24:12.740 --> 24:13.820
The original debtor transferred

24:13.820 --> 24:15.219
the debt to the new debtor.

24:15.300 --> 24:16.219
The new debtor shall fulfill the obligation of repayment to

24:16.219 --> 24:18.820
the creditor.

24:19.219 --> 24:20.020
This is legally called

24:20.020 --> 24:21.820
a debt transfer.

24:22.500 --> 24:23.419
So Mr. Li,

24:24.020 --> 24:26.580
I'll treat you to dinner tonight.

24:47.100 --> 24:47.740
Mr. Xu,

24:48.619 --> 24:50.020
you're doing everything

24:50.020 --> 24:52.500
you can to obstruct us.

24:57.100 --> 24:59.619
Are you together with her?

25:01.219 --> 25:02.580
If you think otherwise,

25:02.699 --> 25:03.780
why are you in such a hurry?

25:08.300 --> 25:09.219
Am I in a hurry?

25:10.300 --> 25:11.500
Aren't you in a hurry?

25:12.340 --> 25:13.580
I see you're in a hurry.

25:19.340 --> 25:22.100
Good. Really good.

25:22.619 --> 25:24.020
When masters face off,

25:24.179 --> 25:25.899
every move is indeed deadly.

25:25.899 --> 25:26.580
Take your hands off me.

25:28.419 --> 25:30.100
So you can see that

25:30.179 --> 25:31.300
the new one

25:31.459 --> 25:32.899
is the love rival of Mr. Xu.

25:33.740 --> 25:35.060
No one but Mr. Chen

25:35.060 --> 25:36.340
could not see it.

25:38.300 --> 25:40.980
You said both of them were so handsome,

25:42.020 --> 25:43.659
it's really hard to choose.

25:45.580 --> 25:46.619
Which one do you support?

25:46.820 --> 25:48.020
I think the new one is good.

25:49.020 --> 25:51.500
Look at how sunny his smile is.

25:52.179 --> 25:54.899
As soon as he enters the door, he called us sister.

25:55.580 --> 25:56.780
What a sweet mouth.

25:57.619 --> 25:58.859
Mr. Xu,

25:59.060 --> 26:00.740
I always feel he puts on airs.

26:02.139 --> 26:03.459
Young girls

26:03.740 --> 26:05.300
like the cold ones.

26:05.820 --> 26:07.580
She will know when she gets married.

26:08.379 --> 26:09.939
Spend the rest of life with

26:09.939 --> 26:11.219
the kind of

26:11.219 --> 26:12.139
cold guy,

26:12.580 --> 26:13.899
how bad she must be.

26:14.699 --> 26:16.179
You're carrying emotion again.

26:16.740 --> 26:17.419
Don't put everything

26:17.419 --> 26:19.020
on your Zhao.

26:19.379 --> 26:20.020
How can Zhao

26:20.020 --> 26:21.419
comparing with Mr. Xu?

26:23.300 --> 26:25.219
That's a career demand

26:25.219 --> 26:26.619
to put on airs.

26:27.740 --> 26:29.219
Although Mr. Xu does not speak much,

26:29.300 --> 26:30.580
but he has done a lot.

26:31.300 --> 26:32.379
He is both gentle and attentive

26:32.500 --> 26:34.060
when looking after people.

26:35.100 --> 26:37.260
He is romantic

26:38.340 --> 26:39.540
but don't talk about it.

26:41.619 --> 26:42.939
I vote for Mr. Xu.

26:42.980 --> 26:43.780
Let's bet.

26:44.379 --> 26:45.139
Bet, bet,

26:45.139 --> 26:46.300
who is afraid of you?

26:46.300 --> 26:47.139
Bet how much?

26:50.699 --> 26:51.459
Half a million?

26:52.340 --> 26:53.139
One million?

26:56.820 --> 26:57.300
When did you have

26:57.300 --> 26:58.419
so many happy beans?

27:00.020 --> 27:01.020
I'll just have half a million.

27:01.139 --> 27:02.100
Okay.

27:02.619 --> 27:03.219
Make a bargain.

27:05.619 --> 27:06.340
Cai,

27:06.939 --> 27:08.980
why do I think the dress of this new handsome guy

27:09.179 --> 27:09.980
is so similar to

27:09.980 --> 27:11.939
your Li Shishan?

27:12.419 --> 27:13.340
I also think.

27:13.859 --> 27:15.379
He looks familiar.

27:18.419 --> 27:21.179
Beijing, Shanghai,

27:22.780 --> 27:25.100
big competitiveness with many people

27:25.619 --> 27:26.740
and high consumption.

27:30.300 --> 27:31.500
Chengdu's

27:33.340 --> 27:34.540
consumption is not low,

27:34.540 --> 27:35.580
and there are also many people.

27:35.939 --> 27:37.619
And I can't eat spicy food.

27:43.619 --> 27:45.020
Li Shishan.

27:45.619 --> 27:46.980
Why didn't you think

27:46.980 --> 27:48.179
you were going to go?

27:52.820 --> 27:53.980
God,

27:55.419 --> 27:56.619
can you tell me

27:56.780 --> 27:58.619
where the hell should I go?

28:37.540 --> 28:38.500
So fast!

28:40.340 --> 28:42.500
It can't be pre-made food?

28:42.820 --> 28:44.139
The tomatoes are fresh.

28:45.540 --> 28:46.619
So the potatoes and

28:46.619 --> 28:47.419
brisket are both premade.

28:49.020 --> 28:49.939
Mr. Xu,

28:49.939 --> 28:51.540
it's a treat to dinner.

28:51.659 --> 28:53.580
It can't be so perfunctory.

28:55.139 --> 28:56.179
You are a big star.

28:57.100 --> 28:58.780
Do you know how long it takes

28:58.780 --> 28:59.740
to stew fresh potato brisket?

29:00.219 --> 29:01.780
Didn't you say you were hungry?

29:04.820 --> 29:06.740
What are stewed on that stove?

29:07.619 --> 29:09.100
It has nothing to do with you.

29:12.500 --> 29:13.699
You have stewed,

29:13.699 --> 29:15.619
so it's okay to share some with me.

29:16.419 --> 29:18.419
Yes, as long as you can wait.

29:53.820 --> 29:54.500
Are you

29:57.179 --> 29:58.300
not satisfied with the taste?

30:00.020 --> 30:01.419
Whether I am satisfied

30:01.419 --> 30:02.619
or not now has nothing

30:02.619 --> 30:03.300
to do with your service attitude or

30:03.300 --> 30:04.580
the food.

30:04.980 --> 30:07.179
Just because I'm hungry.

30:20.659 --> 30:21.780
You have eaten.

30:22.820 --> 30:23.619
Let's talk.

30:24.580 --> 30:25.619
What do I have to talk to you?

30:26.419 --> 30:27.300
Talk about the Entertainment Law.

30:30.139 --> 30:31.219
Talk about Ruan Yu.

30:33.020 --> 30:34.100
What happened in her college.

30:39.219 --> 30:40.340
Do you want to hear

30:40.899 --> 30:42.419
what happened when Ruan Yu was in college?

30:42.780 --> 30:43.899
Or want to hear

30:44.179 --> 30:46.740
what happened when Ruan Yu and I were in college?

30:57.260 --> 30:57.820
Baby,

30:57.820 --> 30:58.659
why are you sneezing?

30:58.659 --> 30:59.459
You have a cold?

30:59.899 --> 31:00.699
No.

31:01.179 --> 31:02.300
It must be you and my father who

31:02.300 --> 31:03.419
are talking about me too much.

31:04.020 --> 31:05.899
Mom, I won't talk to you.

31:05.899 --> 31:07.100
I still have a friend here.

31:07.100 --> 31:08.340
I have to go down and entertain him later.

31:08.780 --> 31:09.619
What kind of friend?

31:10.219 --> 31:11.540
One of my junior students in college, Li Shican,

31:11.540 --> 31:12.859
do you remember?

31:13.540 --> 31:14.260
Right, right, right.

31:14.260 --> 31:14.859
Then he became

31:14.859 --> 31:15.980
a big star.

31:15.980 --> 31:16.780
Yes.

31:17.419 --> 31:18.379
Then don't make him wait for

31:18.379 --> 31:19.219
so long, go ahead.

31:19.899 --> 31:20.939
Not so anxious either.

31:21.139 --> 31:22.699
Well, there's Mr. Xu Downstairs.

31:23.219 --> 31:24.780
Xu?

31:24.780 --> 31:26.139
Xu is in Shen'ao?

31:26.939 --> 31:28.139
Did he come here specifically

31:28.139 --> 31:28.899
to accompany you?

31:30.419 --> 31:31.179
No.

31:31.580 --> 31:33.300
He is here to do public welfare law popularization.

31:33.659 --> 31:34.899
How could you two actually meet?

31:35.219 --> 31:35.740
You know what that

31:35.740 --> 31:36.580
means?

31:36.899 --> 31:37.500
This means

31:37.500 --> 31:39.139
that fate has fallen from heaven.

31:39.139 --> 31:40.219
Okay, Mom won't tell you anymore.

31:40.219 --> 31:40.740
Hang up.

31:40.740 --> 31:41.619
Hurry up

31:41.619 --> 31:42.619
and go with Xu to entertain him.

31:42.619 --> 31:43.859
Okay? Bye.

31:44.820 --> 31:45.419
Mom?

31:51.939 --> 31:52.540
This one is our first time out

31:52.540 --> 31:53.859
to play.

31:54.340 --> 31:55.459
We went to an amusement park and

31:55.859 --> 31:57.219
took a roller coaster ride.

31:58.179 --> 31:59.699
She was afraid so

31:59.899 --> 32:01.459
she just hold my hand tightly.

32:07.419 --> 32:08.300
Just like this.

32:09.219 --> 32:10.780
Hold my arm tightly.

32:13.619 --> 32:14.619
Isn't it a little too much?

32:15.659 --> 32:16.219
Too much?

32:16.419 --> 32:17.780
I think it's pretty normal.

32:20.060 --> 32:20.939
I said this.

32:21.980 --> 32:22.419
This.

32:26.260 --> 32:26.899
This one...

32:27.659 --> 32:29.780
This is a speech in the lecture hall.

32:31.139 --> 32:31.699
She

32:32.100 --> 32:33.899
just look in my direction the whole way.

32:35.659 --> 32:37.659
Only looking in your direction the whole way?

32:39.980 --> 32:41.260
Only smile at my camera.

32:41.780 --> 32:43.300
You see, right?

32:48.100 --> 32:49.340
Only to your lens.

32:54.740 --> 32:55.300
This one.

32:55.659 --> 32:56.820
This picture is of us going camping together.

32:57.580 --> 32:58.179
That day.

32:58.500 --> 32:59.580
Although no fish were caught,

33:00.219 --> 33:02.139
but there's a meteor shower.

33:03.580 --> 33:04.100
You see.

33:04.500 --> 33:05.820
Here's a picture of her making a wish.

33:06.179 --> 33:06.980
How did the shoot go?

33:11.939 --> 33:12.820
What are you looking at?

33:13.659 --> 33:14.699
Looking at pictures from

33:14.699 --> 33:15.459
our college days.

33:16.260 --> 33:17.179
Let me see too.

33:18.859 --> 33:20.379
You've seen it. No need.

33:20.379 --> 33:21.100
Let me see.

33:29.219 --> 33:30.100
Isn't this

33:30.419 --> 33:32.139
the time when I was rehearsing my speech?

33:33.219 --> 33:33.859
That time,

33:33.859 --> 33:35.100
you and Mingying were so bad,

33:35.100 --> 33:36.300
and you made me laugh in the audience.

33:36.619 --> 33:37.619
Fortunately, there were only

33:37.619 --> 33:38.939
two of you in the auditorium,

33:38.939 --> 33:39.580
so there was no embarrassment.

33:40.219 --> 33:40.780
Yes.

33:41.699 --> 33:42.300
Wait.

33:43.740 --> 33:44.780
What did you just say?

33:46.459 --> 33:48.219
I said they made me laugh.

33:48.500 --> 33:49.740
Fortunately, it was only the two of them,

33:49.740 --> 33:50.659
or I would have been embarrassed.

33:55.179 --> 33:56.659
No wonder you only look in one direction.

33:58.340 --> 33:59.139
Look at this.

34:02.100 --> 34:02.699
Look at this.

34:04.379 --> 34:04.939
This...

34:07.300 --> 34:09.179
This was the time you took the roller coaster.

34:09.379 --> 34:10.780
It was the minister and

34:10.780 --> 34:11.619
I who helped you down,

34:11.619 --> 34:12.659
one arm each,

34:12.659 --> 34:13.260
do you remember?

34:14.179 --> 34:15.859
Yeah, it seems like there's something like this.

34:17.780 --> 34:18.619
No wonder.

34:19.540 --> 34:21.219
No wonder you have to hold your arms tightly.

34:22.580 --> 34:23.179
What?

34:23.379 --> 34:24.219
All these little stories

34:24.219 --> 34:25.379
you have told Mr. Xu?

34:26.219 --> 34:26.980
Not only did he say,

34:27.139 --> 34:29.139
he also acted

34:29.139 --> 34:29.980
vividly.

34:30.779 --> 34:31.900
It's a pity not to be an actor.

34:35.060 --> 34:35.580
Right.

34:35.739 --> 34:36.980
I'll see what else?

34:37.779 --> 34:38.460
Look at this.

34:43.819 --> 34:44.540
This one.

34:52.779 --> 34:53.659
There is no more back.

34:57.380 --> 34:58.380
I should still have some pictures

34:58.380 --> 34:59.699
on my phone.

35:16.860 --> 35:18.219
Just a few pictures.

35:18.219 --> 35:18.940
A few.

35:20.460 --> 35:21.139
That's better than someone who

35:21.139 --> 35:22.619
can't even take out one, right?

35:24.580 --> 35:25.580
I...I...I...

35:26.060 --> 35:27.659
I changed my mobile phone after college.

35:27.819 --> 35:29.779
It really seems like I can't find it.

35:30.060 --> 35:31.219
I'm not talking about you.

35:31.219 --> 35:31.819
Come on.

35:32.500 --> 35:33.819
It's not important pictures.

35:34.460 --> 35:35.139
Eat first.

35:36.580 --> 35:37.380
Be careful.

35:37.779 --> 35:38.299
Come on.

35:40.380 --> 35:41.060
Come on.

35:43.060 --> 35:43.699
Mr. Xu,

35:45.739 --> 35:47.860
two bowls for three people?

35:48.100 --> 35:49.339
Haven't you already eaten it?

35:49.739 --> 35:50.460
It's okay for me to have

35:50.460 --> 35:51.380
another meal.

35:51.500 --> 35:52.659
Shican!

35:53.060 --> 35:54.779
Where's Shican?

35:55.460 --> 35:56.460
Shican!

35:58.779 --> 35:59.900
I'm afraid you can't.

36:20.900 --> 36:21.739
Shican!

36:28.299 --> 36:29.100
Shican!

36:33.460 --> 36:34.020
You...

36:35.460 --> 36:36.540
Are you really...

36:37.100 --> 36:38.420
Are you really Shican?

36:39.060 --> 36:39.779
Yes.

36:42.179 --> 36:44.299
I...I finally see the living Shican,

36:44.299 --> 36:44.900
No.

36:45.139 --> 36:47.420
I finally see the real Shican.

36:49.259 --> 36:53.100
I really saw the iron fan too.

36:54.179 --> 36:56.100
The real iron fan is me.

36:56.339 --> 36:57.739
Replacement guaranteed if false.

36:59.819 --> 37:00.580
Shican,

37:01.540 --> 37:03.540
I really didn't expect

37:04.380 --> 37:07.060
that you would come to see me

37:07.380 --> 37:09.219
before I even went to see you.

37:10.980 --> 37:11.819
Did you know?

37:12.100 --> 37:13.420
Today, Mr. Xu told

37:13.420 --> 37:14.420
me that when you came

37:14.900 --> 37:16.699
I was so excited that my phone broke.

37:18.100 --> 37:18.940
Mr. Xu?

37:19.299 --> 37:20.179
Then he must compensate.

37:20.179 --> 37:21.699
No need, no need.

37:21.940 --> 37:23.179
And I have to thank him.

37:23.339 --> 37:24.900
If he hadn't told me you were here.

37:25.139 --> 37:26.940
I'll get on the high-speed rail today.

37:29.100 --> 37:29.900
Shican,

37:35.179 --> 37:35.819
Shican,

37:37.779 --> 37:38.659
Did you

37:39.860 --> 37:43.139
come here specially for me?

37:46.460 --> 37:47.299
So

37:47.940 --> 37:49.139
he came to Shen'ao

37:49.139 --> 37:49.980
because of Li Shishan?

37:50.540 --> 37:51.259
Well, it seems.

37:52.100 --> 37:53.179
He also told me

37:53.339 --> 37:54.819
he came here specially for me.

37:55.259 --> 37:56.339
He was too good at talking,

37:56.339 --> 37:57.420
so I can't believe it at all.

37:58.259 --> 37:59.940
Younger people are like this.

38:01.259 --> 38:02.299
Older ones are not

38:02.580 --> 38:03.420
like this.

38:14.860 --> 38:15.380
Mr. Liu,

38:15.380 --> 38:16.339
I received the repayment

38:16.339 --> 38:17.179
from that trash man.

38:17.219 --> 38:18.219
Thank you for helping me recover

38:18.219 --> 38:19.460
this dirty money.

38:19.460 --> 38:20.819
I'll treat you to dinner another day.

38:22.420 --> 38:24.259
No need. It's a piece of cake.

38:30.540 --> 38:31.339
Hello, ma'am,

38:31.339 --> 38:32.619
are you alone?

38:33.380 --> 38:34.860
Then I will give you a doll to accompany you.

38:34.860 --> 38:35.980
If you need anything,

38:35.980 --> 38:37.100
you can always tell me.

38:37.819 --> 38:38.339
Thanks.

38:38.659 --> 38:39.460
You're welcome.

38:42.739 --> 38:43.500
Hello.

38:43.819 --> 38:44.500
This way, please.

38:48.020 --> 38:48.619
Please.

38:56.179 --> 38:57.659
Let's see what to eat.

39:23.860 --> 39:25.580
I'm sorry. I'm late.

39:26.819 --> 39:27.460
Not too late.

39:28.339 --> 39:29.179
Coming just in time.

39:40.139 --> 39:40.900
Order food, please.

39:41.060 --> 39:42.659
Please order whatever you want to eat.

39:53.460 --> 39:54.179
[How do you know]

39:54.179 --> 39:55.460
[I'm eating hot pot here.]

40:02.779 --> 40:04.179
[Of course I don't know.]

40:04.179 --> 40:05.020
[I just got off work and]

40:05.139 --> 40:06.580
[also come to eat hot pot alone.]

40:07.339 --> 40:09.500
[Well, I'll treat you to this meal.]

40:10.219 --> 40:11.659
[No, no, no, let me treat you.]

40:11.980 --> 40:13.020
[I ordered a bit too many dishes]

40:13.020 --> 40:13.980
[just now.]

40:18.659 --> 40:20.299
[This is my ex-boyfriend.]

40:20.299 --> 40:21.739
[Why are you ordering too much?]

40:22.460 --> 40:23.219
[Because your ex-boyfriend]

40:23.219 --> 40:24.299
[last time mock me,]

40:24.420 --> 40:25.460
[so I have to vent my anger too.]

40:44.020 --> 40:44.659
Chuan,

40:44.940 --> 40:46.619
I think that Australian lobster is quite fresh,

40:46.619 --> 40:47.540
or we also have...Baby,

40:48.179 --> 40:49.020
I remember you are

40:49.020 --> 40:50.259
allergic to seafood.

40:50.619 --> 40:52.380
When did I become allergic to seafood?

40:53.259 --> 40:54.219
Are you confusing

40:54.219 --> 40:55.259
me with anyone?

40:55.460 --> 40:56.900
How is it possible,

40:56.900 --> 40:58.219
baby? You remembered it wrong.

40:59.179 --> 41:00.540
I will never forget

41:00.540 --> 41:02.100
whether I am allergic to seafood or not.

41:07.100 --> 41:09.219
Could you have a bit of insight?

41:09.460 --> 41:11.460
Who has no insight?

41:11.779 --> 41:13.060
I said I want to eat seafood,

41:13.060 --> 41:14.420
why are you pretending to be stupid?

41:14.619 --> 41:15.659
What do you mean?

41:15.659 --> 41:16.380
Zhang Chuan,

41:16.860 --> 41:18.139
you are so mean.

41:18.219 --> 41:19.659
Your ex-girlfriend is so tolerant of you.

41:25.139 --> 41:26.779
I just don't like seafood.

41:26.779 --> 41:27.619
What's wrong?

41:28.060 --> 41:29.020
If you want to eat that Australian lobster,

41:29.020 --> 41:30.020
then order it yourself.

41:33.339 --> 41:34.659
So mean.

41:34.900 --> 41:35.659
Yes.

41:36.500 --> 41:37.259
Go.

41:44.139 --> 41:45.420
Hello. Hello.

41:45.860 --> 41:47.020
Excuse me.

41:47.420 --> 41:49.020
Unexpectedly, we'd

41:49.020 --> 41:49.900
mess up your meal.

41:50.179 --> 41:50.619
Well, I'll treat

41:50.619 --> 41:52.299
you to this dinner.

41:52.420 --> 41:53.060
Then I'll

41:53.060 --> 41:53.819
order the Australian lobster for you

41:53.819 --> 41:55.779
as my apology, okay?

41:55.819 --> 41:56.380
No.

41:57.020 --> 41:58.699
Recognize a person at a meal.

41:58.980 --> 41:59.659
It's worth it.

42:00.219 --> 42:01.139
I have money myself.

42:01.739 --> 42:02.540
I'll order it myself.

42:03.420 --> 42:04.219
Waiter.

42:04.819 --> 42:05.380
Add dishes.

42:10.380 --> 42:11.179
Mr. Liu,

42:12.060 --> 42:12.819
I know why you've been targeted by

42:12.819 --> 42:14.380
the wine bars.

42:15.339 --> 42:17.500
You big spender.

42:17.980 --> 42:19.460
This is too striking.

42:19.659 --> 42:20.739
I am not

42:20.739 --> 42:21.659
always generous.

42:22.860 --> 42:23.580
Where is the love,

42:23.940 --> 42:24.940
where is the money,

42:25.699 --> 42:26.580
Where is the love,

42:26.739 --> 42:27.860
where is the money.

42:27.980 --> 42:28.619
Yeah.

42:29.460 --> 42:30.819
In my opinion, that's the case.

42:33.380 --> 42:34.860
Although the previous woman

42:35.380 --> 42:36.339
is a liar.

42:37.259 --> 42:37.940
But when I was spending

42:37.940 --> 42:38.980
money on her,

42:39.500 --> 42:40.619
I am willing to.

42:41.259 --> 42:42.940
So I didn't hate

42:43.060 --> 42:43.860
and not regret.

42:46.179 --> 42:47.139
Just now.

42:47.940 --> 42:49.020
I forgot to correct you.

42:49.619 --> 42:51.060
How can you called the money you recovered

42:51.299 --> 42:52.659
dirty money?

42:54.020 --> 42:54.659
Those are the sincerity

42:54.659 --> 42:56.060
that we have given.

42:56.779 --> 42:57.980
It was clean.

42:59.259 --> 43:00.020
Later,

43:00.500 --> 43:01.219
stop spending money on those

43:01.219 --> 43:02.339
who don't deserve it.

43:02.980 --> 43:03.659
That's right.

43:04.659 --> 43:07.219
But sincerity is easy to change.

43:07.219 --> 43:08.659
People's heart is unpredictable.

43:09.460 --> 43:10.299
How can you be sure

43:10.299 --> 43:11.060
that the person you

43:11.060 --> 43:12.259
love is worth it?

43:15.339 --> 43:16.179
I really know

43:16.179 --> 43:16.940
that there is such a person.

43:16.940 --> 43:18.020
If you love her,

43:18.460 --> 43:19.259
definitely worth it.

43:20.179 --> 43:20.739
Who is it?

44:11.380 --> 44:13.580
[I will go out to visit today and return in the evening.]

44:18.940 --> 44:19.819
Who asked him?
